{"tid":1560912,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[求置頂］香港人入！和理非更加要入！","createTime":"2019-09-11T11:44:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T11:45:58.000Z","uid":311380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e6f8e4d4f7c381db9293ae3e21eaedcbe455216c","tid":1560912,"uid":311380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:44:54.000Z","msg":"各位，可唔可以真係勇武抗爭？<br />\n有時候我對住香港人應該嬲好定話佢地可愛好<br />\n我知大部分人都唔想用武力 暴力去對抗popo/藍絲<br />\n但和理非 可唔可以唔好阻止勇武去反擊？<br />\n遇到藍絲襲擊/popo落單 我地係應該打柒佢<br />\n點解？ 你諗下我地被人捉/選擇結束自己生命既手足<br />\n你就會知點解<br />\n<br />\n我相信勇武唔似popo會打比人 <br />\n我地要做既只係比佢地知道我地會反抗 <br />\n要佢地唔敢再打我地<br />\n真係唔該和理非唔好再阻止勇武手足<br />\n和理非唔想打就交比勇武<br />\n我可以話你阻止勇武<br />\n你就做緊累死手足既果一班人<br />\n<br />\nFirst aid 手足要做急救可以等藍絲比人打完先<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武手足有分寸，相信佢地好無</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非要行溫和路線我唔反對<br />\n但唔該諗下究竟呢個方法有無用<br />\n我地去到去仍然會比人打<br />\n我地唔反擊就會輸<br />\n<br />\n我始終覺得 唯有暴力先可以贏到呢場戰爭<br />\n我唔想香港人輸<br />\n<br />\nPs 訓醒諗起發夢既內容"},{"pid":"6ab659206af9b76780c203e2d400ead06286eaa7","tid":1560912,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:45:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"}]}